FootnoteText: Data derived from the CDC's National Environmental Public Health Tracking Network. Numerator: Estimated number of each census tract’s population within ½-mile buffer around local parks and beaches from Esri StreetMap Premium/HERE   and state and national parks from the Protected Areas Database of the United States (PAD-US). The estimated population living within ½ mile of a park was summed over all census tracts in a state to estimate the total state-level population residing within ½ mile of a park. Denominator: Census tract and state population from the American Community Survey 5-Year Estimates.
National Environmental Public Health Tracking Network - http://ephtracking.cdc.gov/showHome.action
